:
: PROBLEM: IF A NATIONAL MARKER APPEARS IN THE FACILITY FIELD
:          (IIX C08C MESSAGE), PUF40 ROUTINE WILL EMPTY THE 
:          DIBUF AND FORGET TO RESTORE THE CORRECT FACILITY
:          LENGTH.

PATCH(880818,1400,JWANG,PUF40,,6)
        J       PA1PTR,,
CONPATCH(PA1PTR,,0C)
        JAL     R4,EMPTY,,      :EMPTY DIBUF
        J       PUF05+4,,       :RESTORE CORRECT FACILITY LENGTH)
ENDPATCH(RESTORE CORRECT FACILITY LENGTH IF NATIONAL MARKER APPEARS)
ENDPATCH(IN IIX C08C FACILTY MESSAGE)
